title: Black Ink Crew Charmaine and Ryan Henry
itunes:title: Black Ink Crew Charmaine and Ryan Henry
description:
Today on the show we had two of the cast members from Black Inc Crew Charmaine and Ryan Henry stop by where they spoke on the upcoming season, putting a stop to rumors, Charmaine's bundle of joy and more. Also, we opened up the phone lines to see what would be a reason to stop having relations with your partner and Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man with a tat on the forehead that read "crime pays".
